## Result

After sending the payload to the vulnerable binary, the format string successfully overwrote the `exit` GOT entry.

When the program reached:

```c
exit(0);
```

execution was redirected to the injected shellcode instead of the real `exit()` function.

A shell was spawned with the effective privileges of `level06`, allowing access to the next level.
